      "content": "i dont even know why im typing this. it just feels like everything is gone. 10 years... gone in like an afternoon. i wake up and for a split second i forget, and then it hits me all over again and i just feel like i cant breathe. i cant imagine a single morning without them. it doesnt feel like life is something i can actually do anymore.",
